physicalLayer

Class Cell

  • java.lang.Object
    • physicalLayer.Cell

  • public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to model a position in the 2D environment. A Cell has a Location, and can contain zero or one CellObjects.
    Version:
    v1.2
    Author:
    Chloe M. Barnes
